{"tid":114810,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[中文語法]“除咗XXX之外”，究竟啫係包唔包埋XXX？","createTime":"2017-02-10T05:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T18:52:57.000Z","uid":34701,"like":55,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd69f155c79348fdb43d3c6e155704487ca11d4c","tid":114810,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"成日都諗唔通呢點，好似包唔包都講得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下畀個例子大家揀：<br />\n<br />\n除咗樓主之外，其他人都係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：得樓主係on9，其他人唔係<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：得樓主唔係on9，其他人都係<br />\n<br />\n你哋會點解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d29e40a14846b2bf8ffd739fd1f82dba56bd4ea","tid":114810,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"正評不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee7f9cf246a58de9712536d3a730a13614765c3","tid":114810,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正評嗰欄應該係&ldquo;樓主同其他人一樣都係on9&rdquo;先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打到亂咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7998353ed37158ea5b7f947af1ed7f585e34436","tid":114810,"uid":79706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"&quot;之外&quot; 已經限制主語同賓語係有關系<br />\n故此包括樓主<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n除左樓主， 其他人都on9<br />\n= 不包括樓主"},{"pid":